<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">In the <em sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="63">Drag &amp; Drop Editor</em>, select your desired block that will display the abandoned items.</p>
<ol sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="65">
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="65">Click the <strong sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="65">pencil icon</strong> to edit the settings for the design block.</li>
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">Enable the <strong sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="66">dynamic list</strong> option.</li>
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67">In the <strong sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67">parameter</strong> field, write <code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="67">items</code>.</li>
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="68">In the <strong sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="68">variable</strong> field, write <code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="68">item</code>.</li>
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="69">Set the limit for the number of items that will be displayed. For example, if there are 5 items left in the cart, and you set 3 as the limit, only 3 items will be shown in the email.</li>
</ol>
<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71"><img src="_static/recover-abandoned-carts/items.jpg" sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="71" alt="Email editor"></p>
<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="73">Now add the variables to your email template. In the example above, we have added:</p>
<ul sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="75">
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="75"><code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="75">{{ item.name }}</code> - the name of the item</li>
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="76"><code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="76">{{ item.quantity }}</code> - the quantity of the item</li>
<li sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77"><code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="77">{{ item.price | floatformat: 2 }}</code> - the price of the item</li>
</ul>
<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="79">To add the link of the item, select the <strong sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="79">Call-To-Action (CTA)</strong> button. On the right sidebar, under <em sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="79">Link</em>, type <code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="79">{{ item.url }}</code>.</p>
<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="81"><img src="_static/recover-abandoned-carts/item-url.jpg" sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="81" alt="item.url"></p>
<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="83">To add the image of the item, select the image. On the right sidebar, under <em sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="83">Image source</em>, choose <em sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="83">From URL</em> then type <code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="83">{{ item.image }}</code>.</p>
