<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">Once your design is complete, click the green <strong sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">Save &amp; Quit</strong> button. Then click the <strong sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="87">Save &amp; Activate</strong> button.</p>
