<p sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="119">To add the link of the abandoned cart, select the <strong sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="119">Call-To-Action (CTA)</strong> button. On the right sidebar, under <em sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="119">Link</em>, type <code sourcefile="en/running-your-store/promotional-tools/sendinblue-integration/recover-abandoned-carts.md" sourcestartlinenumber="119">{{ params.url }}</code>.</p>
